Hey, <!channel>! 

Just wanted to let ya'll know that we've been getting traction with our execs in the media this week. <@U0914MEN7> was quoted in an article in Inc. about how to get employees to talk when they stop talking. It came from the rapid response pitching that I mentioned in All Hands last week: <https://www.inc.com/heather-r-huhman/when-fearful-employees-stop-talking-do-these-3-things.html>

Then, <@U026NB2U2> was featured in a PBJ article about his opinions on what the Trump administration is doing with Cuba—specifically regarding Trump's new policy shift: <http://www.bizjournals.com/portland/news/2017/06/19/after-two-years-of-economic-diplomacy-in-cuba-a.html?ana=e_ptl_tf&s=newsletter&ed=2017-06-19&u=cnzz9ML6h8cEBtVtMBZ4Ng0976f265&t=1497906012&j=78411191>
